                        <img src="//wacnppe.blob.core.chinacloudapi.cn/marketing-resource/css/images/home,features,cognitive-services,text-analytics.svg" />
                        <h2>文本分析 API<span>Text Analytics API</span></h2>
                        <h4>检测文本中的情绪、关键短语和语言</h4>
                        <em><a href="/pricing/1rmb-trial/" id="text-analytics_1rmb-trial">申请试用<i class="icon icon-arrow-right-thin"></i></a></em>
